(15, 1, '2022-10-06 07:04:47', '2022-10-06 07:04:47', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jason Fischer nghi ng 5 con c trong gii Cu c Lake Erie Walleye Trail, Cleverland nng tng cng 9 kg, thay v 15,5 kg nh quan st.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng ngi tham d cuc thi hm 30/9 ny cng t ra ng vc,&nbsp;<em>The New York Times</em>&nbsp;a tin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng Fischer l gim c ca cuc thi ny. ng  kim tra v cm thy nh c vt cng khng t nhin trong bng cc con c walleye. \"Chng khng ging nh n nhm \", ng ni.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng ly dao x tht con c. Jacob Runyan, mt thnh vin ca i thi 2 ngi, rn mt theo di qu trnh. Giy pht sau  khin tt c chn ng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'B bi nhi bi st gy chn ng cuc thi cu c  M', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'be-boi-nhoi-bi-sat-gay-chan-dong-cuoc-thi-cau-ca-o-my', '', '', '2022-10-06 07:05:32', '2022-10-06 07:05:32', '', 0, 'https://wordpress.dev/?p=15', 0, 'post', '', 0),
