(20, 1, '2022-10-06 09:02:13', '2022-10-06 09:02:13', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng Nguyn Quang Tun (32 tui, con trai b can Nguyn Phng Hng)  lm n gi cc c quan t tng  TP.HCM  xin khoan hng, gim nh hnh pht ng thi xin bo lnh cho m c ti ngoi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>L do ng Tun a ra l b Hng c nhiu ng gp cho cc hot ng x hi, c bit  giai on i dch Covid-19. Ngoi ra, b Hng ang trong thi gian cha bnh. ng Tun xin cho m c ti ngoi  iu tr bnh cho n khi kt thc v n.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo quy nh ca php lut, b Hng c c hi c ti ngoi trong trng hp ny khng?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Gii thiu v chng ti', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gioi-thieu-ve-chung-toi', '', '', '2022-10-06 09:02:13', '2022-10-06 09:02:13', '', 0, 'https://wordpress.dev/?page_id=20', 0, 'page', '', 0),
